location.fullValue: Palo Verde Plan, New Phase - Arbor at Madera Highlands

data.description: Wow! Look at this home. It has vaulted ceilings, sweeping iron staircase and wide open spaces. You are sure to love this home's floor plan conveniently located by the main park of Madera Highlands. Oversized master suite features ample space for a private sitting area and desk. You also have a custom office on the main floor next to the formal dinning. The finishing touches in this home really make it cozy along with the radiant natural light streaming in from high ceilings & picture windows. There's even a tandem three car garage for that project you're working on and highly sought after storage space! The backyard features premium turf, paver patio, and fireplace to entertain. This home is one you must checkout. It's move in ready so call today and schedule your private tour.
